"{\"uid\": \"swimmingworldmagazine.com-news-reigning-olympic-champ-yui-ohashi-earns-right-to-defend-200-im-title-in-paris\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Reigning Olympic Champ Yui Ohashi Earns Right to Defend 200 IM Title in Paris  After missing out on the chance to defend her Olympic title in the 400-meter individual medley earlier in the meet,Yui Ohashiearned the opportunity to defend her crown in the 200 IM.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23, \"end\": 33, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Ohashi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yui Ohashi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Ohashi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Ohashi\"}, {\"begin\": 72, \"end\": 77, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999926203412901, \"rank\": 7.379713060522554e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the final night of the Japanese Olympic Trials, Ohashi posted a time of 2:09.17 to win the 200 IM and easily get under the qualifying standard of 2:10.70.\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ohashi was followed to the wall byShiho Mastsumoto, who went 2:09.90 to also qualify for the Olympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 530, \"end\": 535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999926203412901, \"rank\": 7.379713060522554e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got so nervous, but I was determined to give 100 percent and see what happens,\\\" said Ohashi, a star at the 2020 Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was confident of swimming well over the second half.\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There were times I thought about giving up in my bid to make the Paris Olympics, but I have come this far with the support of people around me.\\\"\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 866, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Japan also qualified two athletes for Paris in the men's 100 butterfly, where Katsuhiro Matsumoto was victorious in 50.96.\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 868, \"end\": 873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9987375770716219, \"rank\": 0.0009800252873389237, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999926203412901, \"rank\": 7.379713060522554e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 946, \"end\": 965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katsuhiro_Matsumoto\", \"score\": 0.9999998723776652, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katsuhiro Matsumoto\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katsuhiro_Matsumoto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katsuhiro_Matsumoto\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will be joined in the French capital this summer by Naoki Mizunuma, who stopped the clock in 51.23.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1016, \"end\": 1022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9652869995319822, \"rank\": 0.02912992701813198, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Matsumoto 